1
00:00:39,880 --> 00:00:42,160
Wanling Township, west of Chang'an City

2
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:45,480
Is a key hub for Western Regions caravans trading with the Great Tang

3
00:00:46,120 --> 00:00:47,280
Especially the Ten Thousand Nations Inn

4
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:48,840
It is where caravans rest

5
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:51,440
And a bustling place to trade exotic goods

6
00:00:52,040 --> 00:00:53,360
Treasures from the Western Regions

7
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:54,640
Beauties from the Western Regions

8
00:00:55,040 --> 00:00:55,760
Here

9
00:00:56,160 --> 00:00:58,800
You can find absolutely everything

10
00:00:59,080 --> 00:01:01,160
Everyone, everyone

11
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:03,960
This treasure

12
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:06,120
Honored guests

13
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:08,200
What is this thing? What kind of treasure?

14
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:09,440
Watch closely

15
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:15,800
Isn't this just a big painting of a beauty?

16
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:17,480
Yeah, who hasn't seen that before?

17
00:01:17,520 --> 00:01:18,800
I thought it was some kind of treasure

18
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,400
It's just a painting

19
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:21,760
Come down, come down

20
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:22,840
Go down

21
00:01:22,960 --> 00:01:24,360
Come down

22
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:25,360
You

23
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:28,520
Look closer

24
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:55,280
A beauty! A beauty!

25
00:01:58,120 --> 00:02:00,800
Good, good

26
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,240
Good

27
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:06,720
Good

28
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:11,360
What a treasure, what a treasure!

29
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,320
Good, good

30
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,200
Station Master

31
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,440
What happened?

32
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,120
This lowly one is Shen Qinghai

33
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:43,640
I am the Station Master of this inn

34
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:47,800
This was the first time the Ten Thousand Nations Inn was haunted

35
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:49,880
It happened about a month ago

36
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:51,600
My Lord, look

37
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:54,400
Although there are still some merchants at the inn now

38
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:57,640
Compared to when business was booming

39
00:02:58,360 --> 00:03:00,080
It's truly less than one in ten

40
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:01,440
Since there are ghosts

41
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,880
Why do these people still dare to stay at the Ten Thousand Nations Inn?

42
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,360
Wanling Township

43
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:09,040
Is the most convenient route for Western Regions merchants to Chang'an City

44
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,320
If they don't take this road

45
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:11,440
They have to take the mountain path

46
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,000
Which is farther and harder to travel

47
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,360
And there might be wild beasts

48
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:15,960
Weighing the two options

49
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:16,960
They have no choice but to come this way

50
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,840
What this Lord says is very true

51
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,520
As the Station Master

52
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,160
Why didn't you report it to the Magistrate's office?

53
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:26,720
I did go to report it

54
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:29,600
But when the county Magistrate's office heard it was a haunting

55
00:03:29,760 --> 00:03:30,880
They didn't dare to come investigate

56
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:39,200
Then please

57
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:40,920
Take us to the merchant warehouse to have a look

58
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:42,000
Oh

59
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:43,720
This way, please

60
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:52,960
Come

61
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:03,560
Has anyone been killed?

62
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:06,200
That, this lowly one does not know

63
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,960
However, every night after the haunting

64
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,000
Merchants would inexplicably disappear

65
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:13,520
But I don't know if they were scared away

66
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,720
Or taken by the malicious ghost

67
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:21,240
Shentu

68
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:23,400
Did you find anything strange?

69
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:28,640
Vice Minister

70
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:31,920
How about we stay at this Ten Thousand Nations Inn tonight?

71
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,000
You decide

72
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:37,120
Then, Station Master Shen, I must trouble you

73
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:38,360
To spread a message for us

74
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:40,960
Say a wealthy merchant has arrived from the Western Regions

75
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:43,360
Carrying a pearl this big

76
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:45,520
And is staying in Celestial Room No. 1

77
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:48,600
This...

78
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:49,720
This isn't very good, is it?

79
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:51,200
Just do as I say

80
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:53,760
Spread it as far as possible throughout Wanling Township

81
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:54,960
Make it sound as real as possible

82
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,920
As for the truth of the matter

83
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,040
Only the four of us know

84
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,640
If anyone else finds out

85
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:00,600
I will hold you responsible

86
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:03,600
This lowly one understands

87
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,720
Number One Sleuth of the Realm

88
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:23,880
The bait laid out today

89
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:25,360
Is not particularly clever

90
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:27,680
It's not bait

91
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,000
It's just an open strategy

92
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:36,520
The warehouse and the room plaques correspond

93
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,680
Who brought what goods

94
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:40,160
Is all indicated there

95
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:16,200
You mean it's an inside job?

96
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:16,800
That's right.

97
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:19,280
There aren't that many demons and monsters in this world.

98
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:22,600
It's just a cheap trick of playing ghost to kill and rob.

99
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,560
The news about the pearls is out.

100
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:26,160
If a "ghost" comes tonight,

101
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,760
we'll shut the doors and catch the thief.

102
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,520
If no one comes,

103
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:31,520
then someone must have leaked the news.

104
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,600
Then Station Master Shen Qinghai...

105
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,520
...cannot escape suspicion.

106
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:19,920
Didn't I tell you?

107
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,800
People from the Dali Temple are here.

108
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,960
We shouldn't stay here long.

109
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:25,240
Stop knocking.

110
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,480
Why are you still knocking?

111
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:50,760
You are...

112
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:53,640
You aren't...

113
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:55,880
The light's out.

114
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:56,600
The light's out!

115
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:56,960
Ghost!

116
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,400
A ghost!
